"title": "8660: magnifying God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8660: magnifying god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Giving glory to God through worship and through upright living. God's people are exhorted to praise him and to bring honour to his name.</p>\n<h2>Ways of magnifying God</h2>\n<h3>Through praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:19-Ps103:22\">PSA 103:19–103:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:1-Ps33:5\">PSA 33:1–33:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:26\">PSA 68:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:1\">PSA 104:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:1-Ps106:2\">PSA 106:1–106:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:1-Ps111:10\">PSA 111:1–111:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps117:1-Ps117:2\">PSA 117:1–117:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:1-Ps135:3\">PSA 135:1–135:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:19-Ps135:21\">PSA 135:19–135:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:1-Ps150:2\">PSA 150:1–150:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:46\">LUK 1:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:37-Luke19:38\">LUK 19:37–19:38</a></p>\n<h3>In worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:28-1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:28–16:29</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:7-Ps96:9\">PSA 96:7–96:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:1-Ps29:2\">PSA 29:1–29:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:1-Ps100:2\">PSA 100:1–100:2</a></p>\n<h3>Through reverence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:7\">PSA 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:25-Dan6:27\">DAN 6:25–6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:4-Mal2:7\">MAL 2:4–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28-Heb12:29\">HEB 12:28–12:29</a></p>\n<h3>By glorifying him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:1-Ps34:3\">PSA 34:1–34:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:3-Ps63:4\">PSA 63:3–63:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:30-Ps69:31\">PSA 69:30–69:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:12-Ps86:13\">PSA 86:12–86:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:3-Ps96:9\">PSA 96:3–96:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:11-2Thess1:12\">2TH 1:11–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:11-1Pet2:12\">1PE 2:11–2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:6-Rev4:11\">REV 4:6–4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:2-Rev15:4\">REV 15:2–15:4</a></p>\n<h3>By honouring him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:15-1Tim6:16\">1TI 6:15–6:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:13\">ISA 26:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:1-Mal2:2\">MAL 2:1–2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:22-John5:23\">JHN 5:22–5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:19–6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:17\">1TI 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:12\">REV 7:9–7:12</a></p>",
